messages.text: What’s up? How’s your day been?
You just get out of work?
Yeah, yeah. I’m walking to the subway right now.
That’s good. I’m glad to hear it.
I just wanted to ask you something if that’s okay though.
Of course babe, I’m all ears. What’s up?
Okay. Is it alright if I’m a bit blunt then?
I mean, we’e built the last 5 years together on being blunt.
Okay. So, I just have to ask then.
Do you have a foot fetish?
That seems both oddly specific and out of the blue haha.
Well, I was doing some shopping on Amazon a few minutes ago.
I went into the browser history to try to find a page I had went to earlier in the week.
What I found were some links to websites I’d never been to.
Sites that involved women showing off their feet in various positions.
Now, I know only you and me use this computer.
And I’m 99.99%, let’s just call it 100%, sure that I don’t have a foot fetish.
So that really narrows it down to, well, just you, babe.
So do you have a foot fetish or what?
The one time I forget to clear my browsing history…
You actually have a foot fetish?
I’m not tripping here like on our third date when we dropped acid at Coachella?
Don’t hit me with the Bill Murray quotes right now okay?
But yeah babe, I do actually have a foot fetish.
Why didn’t you tell me though when we first started dating?
I guess I just felt uncomfortable telling you because I thought you’d think I was a pervert or something.
And after the first few months, things were going so great I just forgot about it.
I just kept it to myself.
Well, I know you’re a perv already so…
What? You know it’s true, babe.
And I guess I should have told you earlier that I find feet pretty sexy…
No haha. But you could’ve told me at least and I wouldn’t have freaked out.
I really just wanted to know today before I ask you something else anyway.
I just wanted to know if you having a foot fetish explains why I found a folder of pictures of another woman’s feet on your computer too.
What are you talking about babe?
Have you been looking through my computer?
Well, since you were keeping this secret from me for so long, I figured you might be keeping others hidden from me too.
And I was right, wasn’t I?
You’ve been cheating on me with a woman who actually will indulge in your foot fetish?
Am I right or am I wrong?
First of all, don’t look through my computer without me knowing.
Second of all, those are old pictures of my ex babe.
They were from back when we were just friends and I was still going out with her.
And you’ve had them saved on your computer for this whole time?
That’s a bit fucked up, don’t you think?
Babe, you’ve never kept anything one of your ex boyfriends gave you to while you were still dating?
Nope. I mean, you should know by now I’m not very sentimental.
Wow, okay. So you’re a better person than me then.
Is that what you’re trying to say?
I just wanted you to be honest with me about whether you’ve been cheating on me or not.
Well, I am being honest with you when I say I absolutely haven’t.
Because I have something to tell you too.
Have you been cheating on me or something haha?
You haven’t actually been cheating on me have you?
How long have you been cheating on me for?
So how did you expect this to play out in your head?
I would admit I’ve been cheating on you first.
Then you’d admit you cheated on me and then we’d both agree to break up or something?
I just don’t know if I’m ready to forgive you.
I would really hope you do.
And let me just say right now, I stopped it a week ago.
I haven’t being seeing him since.
Or anybody else for that matter.
I know it doesn’t excuse my actions though.
You know what, can we talk about this more when I get home?
I have a long drive ahead of me.
How about we don’t keep anymore secrets from each other. Promise?
We both have a lot to think about now, I guess.
I’ll see you when I get home then.
I know it must not have been easy.
